item.title: FAQ
item.description: Why yet another newsletter? Why not? I want to share my learnings and experiments with others. Usually I will tweet them or sometimes blog about them but I want to deliver it to you cutting the signal to noise ratio out there. When can I expect an issue in my inbox? I am expecting to send it once in two weeks on Fridays. How is it going to be structured?
